  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nDuring fast sync we respond to all `GetBlockHeader` messages with an empty array of headers.  We however, *may* have the requested headers in our database.\r\n\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nWe should *try* to return the headers that were requested.\r\n",
